In re Resignation of Anderson.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Anderson (1992), 64 Ohio St.3d 1206.]

(No. 92-1141 Submitted July 8, 1992 Decided July 9, 1992.)

The resignation of Mark Edward Anderson, Attorney Registration No. 0020858, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
